NOTE: This script is only a proof of concept, for better performance, use TrueCrack https://code.google.com/p/truecrack/

Bash script to crack TrueCrypt volumes

Spanish Post: http://safetybits.net/2009/12/20/crackeando-volumenes-de-truecrypt/

Requirements:
=============
TrueCrypt must be installed!

Usage:
======
$ ./tcracker.sh /path/to/truecrypt/volume /path/to/dictionary

